Package: asterisk-core-sounds-uk
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Ukrainian core Asterisk sound prompts
 Ukrainian-language recordings of Asterisk's core sound prompts (system
 messages, digits, letters, phonetic alphabet, dictation, and Follow Me
 prompts), in alaw/g722/gsm/sln16/ulaw/wav formats.
 .
 Installs into /var/lib/asterisk/sounds/uk_UA, matching the "uk_UA"
 custom Sound Language convention used by FreePBX's Sound Languages
 module - install this package, then select it as a Sound Language in
 FreePBX (registering "uk_UA" there first if it isn't already).
